e of the face.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, of course, the hair, for sure.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, it has the bangs that are the '90s,\\\" Yamaguchi said, chuckling.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2002, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamaguchi_Prefecture\", \"score\": 0.9839543877067621, \"rank\": 0.01588792009158425, \"text\": \"Yamaguchi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamaguchi_Prefecture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamaguchi_Prefecture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Yamaguchi became a household name in the '90s, most Asian American children were growing up feeling like toys-are not-us kids.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.999537709120462e-13, \"text\": \"Asian American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.999537709120462e-13, \"text\": \"Asian American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you were an Asian parent looking for an Asian doll in the U.S., you likely turned to independent mail-order companies or waited until you were visiting your country of heritage.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_people\", \"score\": 0.7842382180289983, \"rank\": 0.27507584922003525, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asia